page.title: 07BEAULIEU MOTOR MUSEUM
page.content: The Motor Museum is in {Beaulieu. In the Museum they have cars of all makes.Most of them are{originals}but some are{replicas.}For instance,{Blue {Bird}which can go{360 m/p/h.}It was involved in a{crash }and was totally destroyed.There is now a replica of the car in the Museum.There are lots of things to do in the Museum besides looking at{cars,}you can have rides on a model railway go on a funfair as well. There is a new thing being introduced at the Museum called{ {wheels.}It is about the changing fashion of{motorcars. In the Museum they also have cars which advertise.They have got a car that is in a shape of a{sauce bottle {and}another car shaped like an{orange.
